{"tid":2499093,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本地零確診一日即「斷纜」屯門及將軍澳各有初步確診","createTime":"2021-04-21T15:17:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T15:46:03.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1cd7ca48d1a082fc1eb46fd81cdfe4da40a9b6b5","tid":2499093,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:17:13.000Z","msg":"本港疫情稍緩，今日（21日）只增1宗輸入個案，是大半個月以來再次本地零確診，但一日即「斷纜」，食物及衞生局晚上公布強制檢測公告，屯門新圍苑新碧閣及將軍澳新寶城第4座，各有住戶初步確診，居民及訪客需於本周五(23日）或之前接受強制檢測。另早前兩度納入強檢公告的屯門友愛邨愛暉樓第 3 座，當局指，由於病毒潛伏期有機會較長，須進行第3次檢測。"},{"pid":"720db91ab256611d53942715ccb554b56d619e28","tid":2499093,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:30:22.000Z","msg":"潛伏期定係支那公司/技術 根本唔準確"},{"pid":"d14f73fad12eaa33476a5ffce36228c7abaa7494","tid":2499093,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:42:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">嘥鳩氣</span>"},{"pid":"571f44b6cad36211fe4270f72737c4cdda48e94e","tid":2499093,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲 on9 諗清楚所謂 「零確診」係乜先啦<br />\n<br />\n零確診 只係代表 搵唔到新個案咋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係代表香港無哂支那病毒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eab9c1a7776c15c6ceaee5b639805e1cd4fd75c","tid":2499093,"uid":29093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:46:03.000Z","msg":"狗政府同啲官喉舌  <br />\n成撚日用 零確診嚟打飛機 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}